SUMMER BRENNAN: A tiny bit.

00:01:09.610 --> 00:01:10.150
CHRIS MANNING: What's that?

00:01:10.150 --> 00:01:10.820
SUMMER BRENNAN: I
said, just a tiny bit.

00:01:10.820 --> 00:01:12.361
CHRIS MANNING: Yeah,
just a tiny bit,

00:01:12.361 --> 00:01:15.580
