So I love oysters, and yes, I
actually like them just raw.

00:20:52.990 --> 00:20:56.104
So that's my favorite
way to have them.

00:20:56.104 --> 00:20:57.520
But I like especially
if they have

00:20:57.520 --> 00:21:00.910
a little bit of the liqueur
still left in the shell.

00:21:00.910 --> 00:21:02.250
So yeah, I eat oysters a lot.

00:21:02.250 --> 00:21:02.750
It's great.

00:21:02.750 --> 00:21:03.820
They're really
having a renaissance,

00:21:03.820 --> 00:21:04.829
especially in New York.

00:21:04.829 --> 00:21:07.370
It almost seems like everywhere
has an oyster happy hour now.

